@host = http://localhost:5204

### 📋 List all available endpoints
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### ❌ Scenario 1: User — username is already taken
POST {{host}}/api/scenario1/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "username": "admin"
}

### ❌ Scenario 2: Order — unknown product + total exceeds sync/async limits
POST {{host}}/api/scenario2/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Unknown",
  "quantity": 1000,
  "unitPrice": 120,
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 3: MoneyTransfer — same-account transfer + insufficient funds
POST {{host}}/api/scenario3/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "checking",
  "toAccount": "checking",
  "amount": 1000
}

### ❌ Scenario 4: Event — confirmed dates + TBD title + end date beyond service limit
POST {{host}}/api/scenario4/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "TBD Kickoff",
  "startDate": "2099-01-01",
  "endDate": "2099-01-02"
}
